This package is for offline battling.

Animation -> Animation class to draw Creature animations such as hit, hurt, death.
Attack -> Object to help the 'attack' GAME_STATE. Stores creature information, along with the computation of hit amounts.
BattleActivity -> Activity to manage the battle logic.
Creature -> Holds information for a creature such as health, attack speed, and image.
DrawingPanel -> The drawing canvas for the battle app.
DrawingPanelListener -> Allows DrawingPanel to commmunicate with the BattleActivity object
GameThread -> Main thread to manage FPS, rendering, and updating.
InfoBar -> item to manage bottom ButtonView / TextView. Switches visiblity of text and buttons as needed.
ResourceManager -> Contains static functions to load resources.
TextWriter -> Extension of TextView to make written text scroll when posted.
